    "en": {
      "title": "A shipload of 92 octane gasoline will be unloaded today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Electricity and Energy, said that the deficiencies in fuel distribution have been corrected and more stocks have been released in the last 4 days.",
        "From his Twitter account, he says that 4000 mt of diesel and 3000 mt of petrol are distributed daily through the Ceylon petroleum storage terminal.",
        "He also said that the fuel requirement for buses and school services has been completed and 35,000 metric tons of 92 petrol will be unloaded tonight."
      ],
